      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still shines beautifully, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and all electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
