    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone looking for utility over aesthetics. While it shows some noticeable cosmetic wear on the exterior and the interior upholstery has seen better days, the engine and transmission are functional and have been regularly serviced. It has some minor mechanical quirks typical for its age, but it remains a solid, drivable car that gets the job done without any major immediate repairs needed.",
