      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. Every detail, from the pristine exterior finish to the meticulously maintained interior, demonstrates an uncompromising commitment to excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a singular opportunity. We invite rigorous professional inspection to confirm its museum-grade status.",
